biases and data quality or probability of publication. These results illuminate the need for greater visibility of citizen science practices with respect to the requirements of biodiversity science and show that addressing bias among scientists could improve application of citizen science in conservation.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Burgess, H. K.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "DeBey, L. B.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Froehlich, H. E.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Schmidt, N.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Theobald, E. J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ettinger, A. K.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "HilleRisLambers, J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Tewksbury, J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Parrish, J. K.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Chapter 6", "biodiversity", "environment assessment", "IPBES", "Alien Invasive Species Assessment AIS", "invasive species"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/83a46bb6ea90ef157daeef84a19ad33b", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/08de191603feb91da273fedd30e5ae6a91fddb91a052d2beaddaecbdfdc47fb0", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/2352922/items/822RE9SG", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/2352922/items/822RE9SG", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/b79e4fcfebf578895353c7ba22874284!/b201596-205459", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/359bd494433933b868f85e88d3437f76", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.1016/j.biocon.2016.05.014", "relation": "isVariantFormOf", "resource_type": "publication", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.7430682", "relation": "isCitedBy", "resource_type": "publication-report", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledB